This is the Passthrough_DigitalRF_Writer-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the Passthrough_DigitalRF_Writer blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'Passthrough_DigitalRF_Writer', which is imported as:

    import Passthrough_DigitalRF_Writer

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(Passthrough_DigitalRF_Writer)
